WEBVTT

00:08:59.567 --> 00:09:00.971
for something better.

00:09:00.995 --> 00:09:03.233
My hope is that within my lifetime,

00:09:03.257 --> 00:09:07.051
I will see what living
as one world actually means,

00:09:07.075 --> 00:09:08.266
that by uniting,

00:09:08.290 --> 00:09:10.413
we will be able to safeguard democracy,

00:09:10.437 --> 00:09:12.027
to protect the environment,

00:09:12.051 --> 00:09:14.587
to save lives by sharing vaccines,

00:09:14.611 --> 00:09:16.942
to create safer routes for migration,

00:09:16.966 --> 00:09:19.023
among many other achievements.

00:09:19.047 --> 00:09:21.312
I don't know whether
I have the one solution --

00:09:21.336 --> 00:09:22.839
no one does.

00:09:22.863 --> 00:09:25.013
I don't know whether
NOW! will be successful

00:09:25.037 --> 00:09:26.786
in achieving these goals.

00:09:26.810 --> 00:09:28.591
But this is not the point.

00:09:28.615 --> 00:09:32.337
The point is that you should take action
to effect change on the global scale.